      "2": 1.30,
      "3": 1.14,
      "4": 1.50 
      },
      "notes": "Incidence ~3.4–6.3%. Rises with impaction depth and pericoronitis. Age and host factors slightly increase risk.",
      "references": [
        "https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/0278239185903313",
        "https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S027823910300836X"
      ]
    },
